content.text: As of the latest available data, institutional investors hold a significant portion of KBWR stock. These institutional investors include mutual funds, pension funds, and other institutional entities. Their ownership reflects the interest of large-scale investment firms in KBWR stock.

Insider ownership represents the shares held by individuals who are closely associated with the company, such as executives, directors, and other key personnel. It indicates the level of confidence and alignment of interests with the company's performance.

The major shareholders of KBWR stock consist of both institutional investors and insider ownership. The specific details and distribution of major shareholders can be obtained from authoritative sources like SEC filings and company reports.
